<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> des
                                <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, und des
                            <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darauf <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan und was uns von im
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu antwurt wirdt, das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun. Denn
                        wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
